data.description: Welcome to this stunning property located in the peaceful town of Bertram, Texas. Come nestle on Apache Trail, this home offers a perfect blend of modern living and natural beauty. This appealingly home sits on 5 plus unrestricted acres of land. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and spacious open floor plan.Four bedrooms, Two bathrooms, feature master with elegant one of kind bath and glassed in shower with gorgeous tile. This Property has a charming kitchen with stainless appliances and spread out family room. Private gated fence for storage for your vehicles.Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this beautiful property home. Schedule your showing today and see all that it has to offer! No Deed Restrictions!
